    "These are test purchases only. Want to support development? Download from the App Store to leave a real tip. [Open App Store](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id6753017503)" : {
      "comment" : "A notice displayed below the tip jar, explaining that the tips are for testing purposes only and that users can only use them to support the app development.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Disse er kun testkøb. Vil du støtte udviklingen? Download fra App Store for at give et rigtigt bidrag. [Åbn App Store](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id6753017503)"
