      }
    },
    "This will delete all downloaded audiobooks and ebooks. You can re-download them later." : {
      "comment" : "A description below the \"Clear All Downloads\" button in the storage preferences view, explaining that clearing the downloads will delete all downloaded audiobooks and ebooks, but they can be redownloaded later.",
